AVerMedia ( Chinese : 圓剛科技 ) is a design and manufacture of Digital Multimedia Video Convergence Technologies including both digital and analog TV tuners , PC - to - TV converters , document cameras and security . In addition to the headquarter office and manufacture of AVerMedia located at Taipei Taiwan , the AVerMedia has branch offices over around Europe , Asia , and North America to serve both end users and OEM / ODM customers . Ranked the 599th of Revenue and the 90th of the ratio of profit after taxes in Taiwan Top1000 Manufacturing sector by Common Wealth Magazine and the 579th and the 97the by Business Weekly . Founded AVerMedia Technologies , Inc . This article is uncategorized . Please categorize this article to list it with similar articles . 